data.description: RARE FIND...2.5 ACRES...JUST 5-MINIUTES TO ALL CASTLE SCHOOLS AND SHOPPING...4-Large Bedrooms + Nursery + Office + Huge Bonus Room...Oversized 3-Car Garage + Large Separate Workshop Area ( 17 x 11)...Back Yard is Completely Fenced with Nice mature trees...The Kitchen is Huge with Tons of Cabinets + Island Center Workspace + an Adjoining Formal Dining Room + Separate Breakfast Nook...The Master Bedroom includes a Large En suite and a Big Walk-in Closet + Adjoining Room which could be used as a Nursery...The Bedrooms are Split Design and Offers Lots of Privacy...The Upper-Level Huge Bonus Room (30 x18) has a Built-in Wet Bar...For Peace of Mind a 2-10 Supreme Home Warranty is in Place...Large Deck (21 x 21) Overlooks Back Yard...Taxes shown are without Exemptions Per State Calculator should be $3421 with Exemptions...Seller will Complete Improvements (See Attached Estimates) with an Acceptable Offer...Don't Miss Seeing This One!!
